r.com/wednesday-final-ratings-survivor-winners-at-war-on-cbs-rises-slightly-from-fall-premiere-of-island-of-the-idols/|archive-date=February 22, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> 27,<ref name=\"3.04\">{{cite web|last=Pucci|first=Douglas|url=https://programminginsider.com/wednesday-final-ratings-record-high-democratic-debate-viewership-with-debut-of-michael-bloomberg-on-presidential-candidates-debate-stage/|title=Wednesday Final Ratings: Record-High Democratic Debate Viewership with Debut of Michael Bloomberg on Presidential Candidates Debate Stage|work=Programming Insider|date=February 21, 2020|access-date=March 28, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307191337/https://programminginsider.com/wednesday-final-ratings-record-high-democratic-debate-viewership-with-debut-of-michael-bloomberg-on-presidential-candidates-debate-stage/|archive-date=March 7, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> 28,<ref name=\"3.05\">{{cite web|last=Pucci|first=Douglas|url=https://programminginsider.com/wednesday-final-ratings-real-housewives-of-new-jersey-on-bravo-rises-to-season-highs-in-total-viewers-and-adults-18-49-with-tenth-season-finale/|title=Wednesday Final Ratings: ''Real Housewives of New Jersey'' on Bravo Rises to Season-Highs in Total Viewers and Adults 18-49 with Tenth Season Finale|work=Programming Insider|date=February 28, 2020|access-date=March 28, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307191454/https://programminginsider.com/wednesday-final-ratings-real-housewives-of-new-jersey-on-bravo-rises-to-season-highs-in-total-viewers-and-adults-18-49-with-tenth-season-finale/|archive-date=March 7, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> 29,<ref name=\"3.06\">{{cite web|last=Pucci|first=Douglas|url=https://programminginsider.com/wednesday-final-ratings-volcano-live-on-abc-falls-short-of-nik-wallendas-prior-stunt-telecasts/|title=Wednesday Final Ratings: ''Volcano Live!'' on ABC Falls Short of Nik Wallenda\u2019s Prior Stunt Telecasts|date=March 5, 2020|work=Programming Insider|acces